On Wed, 1 Oct 2008, Chris wrote:

> So what's the story behind this video?
>
> How fast were they going and how heavy was the cargo?

It was not a standard test.  It was a test of the facility, not the
vehicle.  They put a full load in the back and ran it much faster than
the standard test, just to make sure that nothing would break in their
facility.
